Package org.cytoscape.dyn.internal.model

Interface Summary
DynNetwork<T> DynNetwork is an the interface to the object that represents a dynamic network composed of CyNodes, connecting CyEdges, attributes, and the respective time intervals AbstractDynIntervals.
DynNetworkFactory<T> DynNetworkFactory is the interface for the factory of DynNetworks and is an event sink.
DynNetworkManager<T> DynNetworkManager is the interface of the DynNetworks manager.
 

Class Summary
DynNetworkFactoryImpl<T> DynNetworkFactoryImpl implements the interface DynNetworkFactory for creating DynNetworks.
DynNetworkImpl<T> DynNetworkImpl implements the interface DynNetwork and provides method and data structures to record and retrieve network dynamic information.
DynNetworkManagerImpl<T> DynNetworkManagerImpl implements the interface DynNetworkManager for managing multiple DynNetworks.
